descript.abstract: This dataset contains point locations for Virginia Department of Game and Inland Fisheries' (VDGIF) fish cultural stations. The coverage includes all VDGIF owned hatcheries within Virginia. These point data were compiled by the VDGIF Fish and Wildlife Information Services (FWIS) from the VDGIF Capital Outlay database.
descript.purpose: To show the general location of VDGIF owned fish hatcheries at broad spatial scales.
